summary: An immersive retexture of Ysgramor's Soup Spoon
descriptionHtml:
There is an item in the game called "Ysgramor's Soup [b]Spoon[/b]" and for some dizare and unknown reason it's actually a [b]fork[/b].
This mod turn it into a spoon.

Quick fact: this mod was made within 30 seconds.
author: Chickenator587
